name: Tres cuadras más (Three more blocks)
description:
During the first pandemic isolation in 2020, like everyone else, the confinement was choking me. I wanted to feel a bit of the wind before the storm. 
I painted this landscape in oil on canvas with the idea of creating a nice place to take a nap.
Now I want to merge it with digital painting.
